descriptionHtml:
The Dark Brotherhood Package is a chest  located in the pool of water under the waterfall in The Dark Brotherhood Sanctuary, I made this package because we all know how annoying it can be to not have certain potions for an assassin, particularly if use automatically join the Brotherhood with Live Another Life mod, the chest contains:

Ebony Dagger of Devouring (2)
Poison Health III (5)
Poison Paralysis III (10)
Poison Stamina III (5)
Potion Stamina V (5)
Potion Health V (5)
Potion Ranger III (10)
Potion Fortify Sneak III (10)
author: Buddy1011
